{"tid":1524474,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"停止送頭，諗諗鬼打鬼work唔work","createTime":"2019-08-31T17:20:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T12:05:17.000Z","uid":66991,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"caf8783f168a121c42723101730a33fe2fef92a6","tid":1524474,"uid":66991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:20:31.000Z","msg":"我有朋友做速龍，佢話班狗反而唔似我地細個起就對警察既正義感同聽到警訊主題曲會毛管動。<br />\n<br />\n佢話班垃圾係為錢為宿舍。<br />\n<br />\n我地既然可以眾籌全球登報，<br />\n<br />\n不如諗諗眾籌懸紅<br />\n1)警察指証警察違法，落到charge，有x萬<br />\n2)成功上庭指証入罪，有double 萬<br />\n3)送中高官違法，成功入罪，x萬<br />\n4)指証有老解扮伴記，x萬<br />\n<br />\n世界冇人可以100%跟著法律走，一定有1%違法eg 稅務、物業、呃福利租津<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入到罪係perfect, 但入唔到，等佢地鬼打鬼，互相猜疑。<br />\n<br />\n職場一定有分派、要分化佢地，好過手足上場比佢地同聲同鬼殺害。<br />\n<br />\n繼續送頭唔係辦法，而且就快到選戰，要人數。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫手推，thanks"},{"pid":"c5f8204b2995bc88ac1ff0e05918c0d823fa91b1","tid":1524474,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:21:25.000Z","msg":"玩得過，p牌都推"},{"pid":"4bd09bcc62b012eedeb3046fc7cb831675461034","tid":1524474,"uid":165871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:26:38.000Z","msg":"喂 屌你正呀喂<br />\n以其人之道還治其人之身 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db18fec82aa0006a7faebe4d8f80a80f747ab329","tid":1524474,"uid":98842,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:28:18.000Z","msg":"而家連黑社會都入唔到罪呀<br />\n721一個都無呀<br />\n<br />\n黑警仲會入罪？夠啦"},{"pid":"c7fd52e9c4e1040727d2b318a38fd63d6c376c4f","tid":1524474,"uid":143230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:31:58.000Z","msg":".咁你朋友唔企出黎?"},{"pid":"a2b39678382f50677a3007109dd1a9465a267c02","tid":1524474,"uid":188906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:48:35.000Z","msg":"想左好耐，推！"},{"pid":"ea65701010d222388fc092fc